installation:
	install node.js
	then:
	$ npm install express
	$ npm install socket.io

running:
	$ node app.js

	if connecting remotely make sure the ip 
	in public/javascript/cards.js matches the ip 
	of the machine running the server



Current server is node.js and express, but i want 
to change it so that ruby on rails handles the web 
serving.

